This is how to prime_fib of n:
   Remember that a is 2
   Remember that b is 3

   When n is 1, then:
      The answer is a
   End when

   When n is 2, then:
      The answer is b
   End when

   Remember that i is 2
   Do this n times:
      Remember that c is sum of a and b
      Remember that a is b
      Remember that b is c
      Increase i
      When i is n, then:
         Leave the loop
      End when
   End do

   The answer is b
